OL,5, A gunman who killed 10 people in a     
OL,6, racially-motivated shooting at a       
OL,7, Buffalo, New York, supermarket last    
OL,8, year has been sentenced to life in     
OL,9, prison at a dramatic hearing.          
OL,11,FPayton Gendron, 19, pleaded guilty to  
OL,12,F25 counts, including first-degree      
OL,13,Fmurder and terrorism motivated by hate.
OL,15,FAhead of the sentencing on Wednesday, a
OL,16,Ffamily member rushed towards Gendron   
OL,17,Fbut was constrained by security.       
OL,19,FFamily members shared emotional impact 
OL,20,Fstatements.                            
